  <p><strong>Quick Answer:</strong> Rosé wine pairs exceptionally well with Mediterranean cuisine, grilled vegetables, seafood, and light pasta dishes. Its crisp acidity and subtle fruit flavors complement foods without overwhelming delicate ingredients, making it perfect for summer dining and versatile enough for year-round enjoyment.</p>
